curl -XPOST 'http://localhost:9200/electronic_products/_create/2992' -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d '{"product_name": "SGM42513", "table_name": "GENERAL DESCRIPTION", "content": "GENERAL DESCRIPTION  The SGM42513 is an integrated driver IC for driving  motors and coils in industrial applications. The IN1 and  IN2 pins allow simple interfacing to controller circuits.  Internal protection functions are provided for under-  voltage lockout (UVLO), over-current protection (OCP)  and over-temperature protection (OTP).   The SGM42513 is available in a Green TSOT-23-6  package. It operates over an ambient temperature  range of -40℃ to +125℃.        "}'
